Package: lua5.1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simple, extensible, embeddable programming language
 Lua is a powerful, light-weight programming language designed for extending
 applications. LNUM patch is applied to this version of Lua.
 .
 This package contains the Lua command line interpreter.

Package: luac5.1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simple, extensible, embeddable programming language -- bytecode compiler
 Lua is a powerful, light-weight programming language designed for extending
 applications. LNUM patch is applied to this version of Lua.
 .
 This package contains the Lua bytecode compiler.

Package: liblua5.1-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: liblua5.1-0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Section: libdevel
Description: Simple, extensible, embeddable programming language -- development
 Lua is a powerful, light-weight programming language designed for extending
 applications. LNUM patch is applied to this version of Lua.
 .
 This package contains developer resources for using the Lua library.
 Install it if you are developing programs which use the Lua C API.

Package: liblua5.1-0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Section: core
Description: Simple, extensible, embeddable programming language -- shared library
 Lua is a powerful, light-weight programming language designed for extending
 applications. LNUM patch is applied to this version of Lua.
 .
 This package contains runtime libraries.  You shouldn't need to install it
 explicitly.

Package: liblua5.1-0-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, liblua5.1-0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Section: debug
Description: Simple, extensible, embeddable programming language -- debug symbols
 Lua is a powerful, light-weight programming language designed for extending
 applications. LNUM patch is applied to this version of Lua.
 .
 This package contains the debugging symbols for liblua5.1, lua5.1 and luac5.1
